This artifact vendors the "writing-plans" skill from obra/superpowers.

Vendored file (upstream path):
  - skills/writing-plans/SKILL.md

References to un-vendored sibling skills (subagent-driven-development,
using-git-worktrees, finishing-a-development-branch) were softened to optional
notes so this artifact stands alone; the default plan-save path was changed
from `docs/superpowers/plans/` to the per-feature spec folder
`docs/specs/NN-slug/plan.md` (co-located with its spec, tracked via meta.yaml).
The planning discipline is otherwise a faithful copy.

